item.description: It is that time of year again. Come join us for lots of fun. There are six players to a team. The questions are not too hard and the food and drink makes it easier. We have done pretty well in the past. We won pub crawl tickets, hats and t-shirts, a gift certificate to Margaritas and a gift certificate to Kelley's Row. It is a pretty small bar so it will be easy to find the Trailblazers. If you are new the Trailblazers or you have not met me you can email me and I can let you know where we will be. All are welcome and always love to meet new people. Hope to see you there.
